brouillard salin
• Lastwert bis 60kg pro paar
• Überauszug

• Winkel an Schiene zur

• Rastung in geschlossener

Notes:
• Fixing recommendation: 4mm wood screw/
6mm Euro screw
• Load ratings quoted are the maximum for a pair

unless otherwise stated. For more information,
refer to “How to select a slide” section

• Empfohlene Befestigung: Holzschraube 4mm/
Euro-Schraube 6mm
